        "chr_0033_camille_NormalSkill": {
            "Icon": "skillicon/icon_skill_camille_01",
            "Element": "Fire",
            "Name": "Blazing Exorcism",
            "Desc": "Camille summons <@ba.key>Firefang Vesperwings</> that fly towards the enemy to deal <@ba.fire>Heat DMG</> and apply <#ba.fireinflict>Heat Infliction</> on enemies in a small area of effect. The <@ba.key>Firefang Vesperwings</> then temporarily <@ba.key>hover</> around the target and apply <#ba.weak>Weakness</> and <#ba.firevul>Heat Susceptibility</> to the said target for the duration of the hovering. When the target is defeated, the <@ba.key>Firefang Vesperwings</> fly to another nearby enemy, deal <@ba.fire>Heat DMG</>, and apply <#ba.fireinflict>Heat Infliction</>, <#ba.weak>Weakness</>, and <#ba.firevul>Heat Susceptibility</> to the new target.\nHitting an enemy with <@ba.key>hovering</> <@ba.key>Firefang Vesperwings</> with Camille's combo skill sets off an explosion after a short delay. This explosion deals additional <@ba.fire>Heat DMG</>.",
